ygData.subject: Re: Executioners Axe
ygData.msgSnippet: Ok lemme first start off that i was going to accomplish this quest but there is one thing... You have to summon the executioner then kill her. Good luck trying
ygData.messageBody:
Ok lemme first start off that i was going to accomplish this quest but
there is one thing... You have to summon the executioner then kill her.
Good luck trying to kill her unless your around lvl 40 at least.. *sigh*
guess i will have to try again later on. She has DA and hits for around 89
points with each swing... Very Nice weapon.. Very Hard to get.
